</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCB74216A18FFA852E8397E0353FEDD" blockId="15.[151,1436,150,321]" pageId="15" pageNumber="357">
<emphasis id="B900A8336A18FFA852E8397E0627FE81" bold="true" box="[199,308,259,285]" pageId="15" pageNumber="357">Remarks</emphasis>
. This species is distinguished from other 
<taxonomicName id="4C740FA26A18FFA85133397E0445FE81" box="[796,854,259,285]" class="Insecta" family="Lonchaeidae" genus="Silba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="357" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B900A8336A18FFA85133397E0445FE81" box="[796,854,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="357">Silba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species by its numerous short prensisetae and the unique ventrally-directed projections arising from the structures of the hypandrium.
</paragraph>
